com.github.naoghuman.lib.tag.core

Interface TagRelation

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<TagRelation>, Externalizable, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultTagRelation

    public interface TagRelation
extends Comparable<TagRelation>, Externalizable
    A TagRelation is a simple mapping between a container like FlowPane and all Tags which should be shown in this container.

    An instance from this Interface can be easily generated with the fluent builder TagRelationBuilder which is the preferred way to generate an implementation from this Interface.

    Since:
    0.1.0
    Version:
    0.3.0
    Author:
    Naoghuman
    See Also:
    TagRelationBuilder, FlowPane
